        About this item

        • Eau De Parfum for HER. Contains 15% - 20% pure perfume oil and can last up to 8 hours.
        • SCENT PROFILE: This is the fragrance of an exotic evening, where mysteries are revealed and layers unveiled. A passionate awakening of the senses is discovered through the colours of the sunset, slowly blending into the night.
        • FRAGRANCE NOTES: Top Notes - Black Currant, Grapefruit, White Flower Middle Notes - Orange Blossom, Earthy, Iris End Notes - Vanilla, Tonka, Patchouli, Wood
        • ABOUTS US: Liberty Lifestyle is an extension of the Liberty Group, which is an established business house from India; with experience of over 70 years in the shoe industry. All fragrances have been meticulously crafted in France by world-renowned perfumers and manufactured in India.

        How are ratings calculated?
        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
